Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.60,0:00:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight's show is a compilation of clips falling under the theme "Knight Scoop reminds me of ...", and we can't possibly leave out this last category.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.62,0:00:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"Knight Scoop reminds me of 'Shock Footage'!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The following 'Shock Footage' would be unthinkable on any show other than Knight Scoop, please take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,," ... comes from the 34 y/o Kitamura Takashi, a company employee living in Osaka."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.42,0:00:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"I haven't had a girlfriend in 34 years."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm not very good-looking, so I was never popular and never had a girl confess her love to me."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"I've already given up on ever getting married."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"I've decided on spending my life alone."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"I have accepted my fate and come to terms with the truth that I will never have a girlfriend."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.16,0:00:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"But, I'd like to go on a date, even if it was just for one day. The gender doesn't matter."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:01:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"Detectives, won't you please go on a date with me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he's already waiting over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(630.857,615.143)}Meeting the client
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.70,0:01:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitamura? - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Takeyama. - I'm Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.18,0:01:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're with Tantei Knight Scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'd like to go on a date? - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.36,0:01:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And whether it's with a man or a woman, ... - It doesn't matter, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am ... - The girlfriend, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.14,0:01:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm the girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How come, in the hopes of getting a date, did you consult the Detectives instead of going marriage hunting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I've tried that! It was no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to marry, but it's just not possible for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.78,0:01:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so you've come to think it's not possible? - Yes, so even if it's just one time, a single time, I want to go on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:02:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So for this date, the gender doesn't matter to you ... - Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all! - Not at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So even with me ... - Is completely fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it clearly, Takeyama, please, I want to go on a date with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to go on a date with me? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we call each other? - Call me Ta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh? - Call me Ta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be Take-chan? - Yes, Take-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, shall we go on a date, Ta-kun? - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it, Take-chan! - So do I. What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we climb up there? - Yes, I'd like to go up and see the view.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(252.571,615.143)}Hanging gardens
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting nervous. - Ah, when it goes up like that. - You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not so good with heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(616,555.714)}Setting
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(396.572,608.286)}More than friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(849.143,604.857)}but less than lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah is that so? - That's why I'm a bit nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we've come up here, is there something you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like how our lives will progress from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,While looking at this view?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-kun, how would you like to live your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How I would like to live my life ... ? - What you're thinking of right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I do want to get married ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you say you couldn't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My appearance ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So your complex about your appearance is the main factor? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My head, mostly ... - Your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hair? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are plenty of people who are popular, even after becoming bald.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And your head has come a long way, at 34 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there somewhere you want to go next?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:04:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really for me, but you asked for the date, so if there's somewhere you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.18,0:04:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Something I ... a photo booth to take pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one should we take?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-kun, you pick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! - It'll take 4?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,H-how?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't we hold hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, how would you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best if you don't go straight for it, but gradually work your way up. - Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this ... or more like this ... ? - Nah, well, this won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I just held onto here and walked behind ... - No no no no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I ... - NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That was scary! You're scaring me if you say it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden you became really scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,How about Yakiniku? Even if it's still early. - That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,One serving of sirloin ... and one serving of pork rib ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you feed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it like, being fed for the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt good. - It did?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have any experiences like that with women?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I have kissed before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, in Gunma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In Gunma?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:06:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,At a hostess club. - A hostess club?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was your first kiss then? - I didn't feel anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't feel anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it wasn't with someone I loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to actually go on a date with a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So even if this was the date now ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,... I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're happy because you've been on a date with me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do after our meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to spend a little more time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to have a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't kissed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:07:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? - It doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that matter the most? - It doesn't! It's just about going on a date with me, kissing me, ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you do it with me it won't be sincere, and isn't that like your last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, people will recognize me. "Ah, it's that guy, Takeyama, he went overboard today!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What about when we held hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When we held hands, you thought of it that way? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ok if it's with you. - It's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not ok, anyway you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've already done a lot, it'll only cause trouble for this shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But at night, this would be a good place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:08:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't just decide by yourself "We'll do it"! You're being presumptuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it! - No, not "let's do it"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That was too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the date complete with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's become clear to me in that position, is that you've given up too soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You hardly have any confidence in yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten way too worked up about yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a good personalty and a nice face, you can definitely find love!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home! Honestly, go home, this shoot is over!

